high_descs: Turn right to face the tomato on the table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Bring the tomato to the microwave in front of you.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Take the heated tomato back across the room to the small black table in the opposite corner on the right.
Put the heated tomato on the right side of the black table, in front of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the small black table.

high_descs: Go around to the left side of the table in front of you.
Pick up the tomato, to the left of the potato, on the table.
Turn to your right and go back to the front of the table where the microwave is.
Place the tomato in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around and go across the kitchen to the white table, then turn to your right and go to the small, black shelf to the left of the counter top.
Place the tomato behind the apple on the small, black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato on the black shelf.

high_descs: Turn toward the table with the tomato and microwave on it
Pick up the tomato from the table
Move around the table to face the microwave on the left
Open the microwave door, put the tomato inside and close the door. Turn on the microwave, open the door and take the tomato out of the microwave
Turn left and head to the table to the left of the sink on the right
Put the tomato by the sponge on the small table with shelves
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on a table
